STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Miguel Angel LORENZO BALTAZAR, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0677 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Miguel Angel Lorenzo Baltazar appeals his conviction for murder in the first degree. REVERSED AND REMANDED FOR NEW TRIAL.

REVERSED AND REMANDED FOR NEW TRIAL.
